Filipino Student Association.description: The purpose of UTD FSA is to unite students who are interested in promoting the Filipino-American culture and to share, display, and preserve the Filipino-American culture as an organization. UTD FSA engages in cultural-based and social activites and is involced in philanthropic endeavors as well. Aprart for that, UTD FSA offers community acitivites and oppurtunites including competeitive and non-competitive sports and dance teams.
